    {
      "paragraph_name": "1000-INITIALIZE",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This paragraph initializes the program environment. It retrieves the MQ trigger monitor data (MQTM) from CICS, which contains the MQ queue name and trigger data. It moves the queue name and trigger data to working storage. It sets the wait interval for MQGET to 5000. It then performs 1100-OPEN-REQUEST-QUEUE to open the MQ request queue and 3100-READ-REQUEST-MQ to read the first message from the queue. This paragraph prepares the program to begin processing authorization requests.",
      "called_by": [
