      "purpose": "This paragraph reads a customer record from the VSAM file identified by WS-CUSTFILENAME. It uses the XREF-CUST-ID to build the key (WS-CARD-RID-CUST-ID) for the READ command. The paragraph checks the CICS response code (WS-RESP-CD) to determine if the read was successful. If the record is found (NORMAL), it sets FOUND-CUST-IN-MSTR to TRUE. If the record is not found (NOTFND), it sets NFOUND-CUST-IN-MSTR to TRUE, logs an error message to the error log, and sets error flags. If any other error occurs during the read, it logs a critical error message including the CICS response and reason codes to the error log. It calls 9500-LOG-ERROR to log errors.",
